  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThe Keycard PIN input can give the impression that it is in focus when it is not. For example when the modal is open the first position will be flashing but will not actually accept any input.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50769329/206020003-ee4233bd-12d5-43b8-8083-7a9295d4aa44.png)\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nHave the keycard PIN entry modal open but the PIN entry field out of focus via tab/click.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nUsers can easily tell if the PIN entry field is in focus or not so the app behaves as a user may expect\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nNo input is registered by the field and it is not obvious to the user that the field is not in focus. \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: 0.8\r\n- Operating System: Mac\r\n\r\n",
